text: Visited the new stall “ Yi Xuan Seafood”. Ordered 3 dish only . Veg over cook , meat still raw and omelette is undercook and way too salty. Service also bad.
nice food court. Clean and convenient. I like curry fish head there.

Tried the new Thai stall, tomyum soup is very nice, sour enough, creamy. Basil rice a bit salty and rice is dry, but the omelette is nice. Thai style tofu is crispy and tasty sauce. Will come back and try another dishes. Reasonable price w set meal.
Came here to buy satay and mee hoon kueh.

Good variety of good yummylicious food situation in this coffeeshop!

Must-trys: Popiah, Wanton Mee, Satay, Hokkien Mee

🌯 Personally loved their Popiah here! 😋👍🏻 Must-order and I always dabao back home. Ingredients and “man guang” are fresh, not overly seasoned, blends well together and nicely wrapped! Recommend to add chili, not overly spicy but yet giving that extra spice aromatics! Really slurps just writing this review! 🤤

🥟🍜 Yummylicious Wanton Mee! Springy saucy noodles, thick char siew and meaty wantons.

🍜🦐🍗🍢 Hokkien Mee and Satay are good too! My easiest and nearest crave fix for Hokkien Mee and satay.
